snippet.title: Celebrities Finally Speak About Working With Amber Heard "I Wanted To Quit"
snippet.description:

Celebrities Finally Speak About Working With Amber Heard "I Wanted To Quit."

In 2016, actress Amber Heard filed for her divorce, claiming her Ex-husband Johnny Depp had abused her physically and even mentally through her relationship with Hollywood star Johnny Depp. Since then, Johnny Depp has been removed from quite a few Hollywood projects, including the Pirates of the Caribbean franchise and the Fantastic Beasts franchise.

Many Hollywood actors and biggies have proved Amber Heard's allegation on Johnny Depp.
